Suzi Parker &quot;1000 Best Bartender's Recipes&quot;
Sourcebooks, Inc. | 2005-08-01 | ISBN: 1402205473 | 576 pages | PDF


1000 Best Bartender's Recipes is a fun, sassy, home bartending guide that will make even the most novice bartender look like an expert. Packed full of drink recipes and tips for all occasion-and all times of the day-this new 1000 Best book will have readers experimenting with, and adding to, their liquor stash.

From a Bloody Mary in the morning to guaranteed hangover cures, 1000 Best Bartender's Recipes covers a wide range of drinks such as: Sorority and Fraternity Fantasia Shots for the Chronic Twenty-one-year-old Park Avenue Potions Champagne Concoctions and Fancy Liqueurs Around the World in 100 Drinks Passport Lover's Paradise Bahama Mama Hula 'Til It Hurts Tropical Drinks

For readers who want to learn how to mix, shake and stir at home, 1000 Best Bartender's Recipes is the only book they'll need to keep the party going all night long.
